      "title": "LIOC resumes fuel distribution to filling stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fuel distribution to Lanka IOC filling stations recommenced from today (July 10), the Indian Oil Corporation\u2019s subsidiary in Sri Lanka says.",
        "Accordingly, the company\u2019s terminal in Trincomalee will carry out its operations 24 hours a day."
